    tmp = wp.sin(((v1 + 0.59 * v0 + 0.53) * (tmp + 0.68 + v0 + 0.96)))
    v1 = 0.02
    v2 = wp.sin(v2)
    v1 = wp.abs(wp.cos((v0 + 0.84 - tmp + 0.78)))
